#### Default behavior
* text=auto

#### Maven Wrapper
/mvnw text eol=lf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

#### Shell Scripts
*.sh text eol=lf

#### Java / Spring Files
*.java text eol=lf
*.kt text eol=lf
*.groovy text eol=lf

#### Config / Infrastructure
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.properties text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf

#### Documentation
*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf

#### Binary Files
*.jar binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
